name: SellingSocial
overview:
SellingSocial is an Online Social Networking Platform that is solely for Classified Add Listing & Job Opportunities.

In the Declining U.S. Job Market, With the Design of Selling Social Powerful & Simply to use Platform, users will find it a more favorable experience through the use and combination of tools to Post and Search for Jobs to Careers.

Selling Social.com is uniquely positioned in the Marketplace to take advantage of the current wave of Social Selling, Because many highly recognized business publications, such as Forbes magazine, are stating publicly that the “future of sales in going in this direction.”

Be a part of, “a new trend in Social Networking” by getting on board the most advanced connection site on the web, while having fun interacting with friends and discovering people you share a common interest with.

Oct 18th 2011 Selling Social was announced one of the finalists (10) in Bloomberg Television’s TechStars contest. (Wizora winner) 5/18/2012 Currently, Selling Social is now kicking off it’s new Design and Implantation of 1 click connect for all top social platforms. Selling + Social = Think about it?
